<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no" />
    <title>About Us - Derry World</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/bootstrap.css" />
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="/css/responsive.css" rel="stylesheet" />

    <style>
        .about-section {
            padding: 120px 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .about-content {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .about-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .about-header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .about-header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #666;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .story-section {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 40px;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 80px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .story-section {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        .story-image {
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .story-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
        }

        .story-content h2 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .story-content p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .values-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 80px;
        }

        .values-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .value-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .value-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .value-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #ffbe33;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .value-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .value-card p {
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .team-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 80px;
        }

        .team-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .team-member {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .member-image {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .member-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
        }

        .member-info {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .member-info h3 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .member-info p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .social-links a {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .social-links a:hover {
            color: #ffbe33;
        }

        .contact-section {
            text-align: center;
            background: white;
            padding: 60px 0;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .contact-info {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 40px auto 0;
        }

        .contact-item {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .contact-item i {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #ffbe33;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .contact-item h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .contact-item p {
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>


</head>
<body class="sub_page">
  <div class="hero_area">
    <div class="bg-box">
      <img src="/images/hero-bg.jpg" alt="Derry World Restaurant Hero Background">
    </div>
    <%- include('../partials/user/header-no-bg', { user, cartCount }) %>
  </div>

  <!-- about section -->
  <section class="about_section layout_padding">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="img-box">
            <img src="/images/about-img.png" alt="About Derry World">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="detail-box">
            <div class="heading_container">
              <h2>We Are Derry World</h2>
            </div>
            <p>
              There are many variations of passages of food stories available, but the majority have suffered alteration in some form, by injected humour, or randomised words which don't look even slightly believable. If you are going to use a passage of our menu, you need to be sure there isn't anything embarrassing hidden in the middle of text. All
            </p>
            <a href="#">
              Read More
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <!-- end about section -->

  <!-- footer section -->
  <%- include('../partials/user/footer') %>
  <!-- end footer section -->
</body>
</html>
